{"tid":1762854,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"﻿港大中大撥款抽起﻿﻿ 泛民質疑政治報復﻿","createTime":"2019-11-30T01:47:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-30T03:56:41.000Z","uid":138707,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2f9b36cc8556f620a27c8a69196e6988eaf04b6d","tid":1762854,"uid":138707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T01:47:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/daily/hk/815061/%E6%97%A5%E5%A0%B1-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E6%B8%AF%E5%A4%A7%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%A7%E6%92%A5%E6%AC%BE%E6%8A%BD%E8%B5%B7-%E6%B3%9B%E6%B0%91%E8%B3%AA%E7%96%91%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB%E5%A0%B1%E5%BE%A9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Fdaily%2Fhk%2F815061%2F%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%25A0%25B1-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%2592%25A5%25E6%25AC%25BE%25E6%258A%25BD%25E8%25B5%25B7-%25E6%25B3%259B%25E6%25B0%2591%25E8%25B3%25AA%25E7%2596%2591%25E6%2594%25BF%25E6%25B2%25BB%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E5%25BE%25A9&d=upH1NnktvNch8HeVEtNbY0ngG4XMVyvHznkFIzn%2BcUY%3D&h=c5d50d5d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Fdaily%2Fhk%2F815061%2F%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%25A0%25B1-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%2592%25A5%25E6%25AC%25BE%25E6%258A%25BD%25E8%25B5%25B7-%25E6%25B3%259B%25E6%25B0%2591%25E8%25B3%25AA%25E7%2596%2591%25E6%2594%25BF%25E6%25B2%25BB%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E5%25BE%25A9&h=e87f75a5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/daily/hk/815061/%E6%97%A5%E5%A0%B1-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E6%B8%AF%E5%A4%A7%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%A7%E6%92%A5%E6%AC%BE%E6%8A%BD%E8%B5%B7-%E6%B3%9B%E6%B0%91%E8%B3%AA%E7%96%91%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB%E5%A0%B1%E5%BE%A9</a><br />\n<br />\n香港不少大學生被指參與反修例抗爭，繼理工大學撥款申請抽起後，財經事務及庫務局昨去信立法會財務委員會，決定撤回在中大及港大翻新及興建醫學大樓的撥款項目，合共逾二億五千萬元的撥款。有民主派議員質疑，今次是政府作出政治報復。<br />\n<br />\n中大在大埔第三十九區興建一座教學科研綜合大樓的5,970萬元，以及港大提升設施和發展醫學院校區的1.943億元。<br />\n<br />\n今次是政府兩周內第三度抽起大學工程項目撥款。政府原定本月十五日以「需要更多時間解說」為由臨時抽起理大擴建工程撥款申請。至本月十九日，稱理大因近日事件而需檢視工程時間表。又再抽起擴建理大圖書館的三億四千萬元撥款。<br />\n<br />\n公民黨立法會議員陳淑莊質疑，有人打算要懲罰大學和大學生，又斥抽起撥款會影響醫科生畢業。但有建制派議員曾稱吐露港公路被中大學生堵塞良久，反映大學教育有問題，故對撥款予大學有保留。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">民建聯惡行，成日用政治藉口打壓民生議題，真係唔怪得你今年民選輸到脫褲。</span></strong>"},{"pid":"a3b84b4567f7c1ef1ae3fcf8fc5895cef162afb7","tid":1762854,"uid":36470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T01:57:15.000Z","msg":"煲大佢"},{"pid":"72d403269f4d08a4500c5b7e841f9855b1286abd","tid":1762854,"uid":246764,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T01:59:47.000Z","msg":"推比誠哥鉅哥幫手"},{"pid":"f41323fd941ab1f2330943d40166ea3ea07c2672","tid":1762854,"uid":46746,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T02:00:36.000Z","msg":"小學雞 小家種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b305e999a93b1909d777fd7ac1e68ab34dc2ece","tid":1762854,"uid":149973,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"72d403269f4d08a4500c5b7e841f9855b1286abd","tid":1762854,"uid":246764,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T01:59:47.000Z","msg":"推比誠哥鉅哥幫手"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T02:02:51.000Z","msg":"佢哋講聲撤資裁員<br />\n班官嚇到賴尿啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"744519f7011a2deefc86cffef8eac4c340462c13","tid":1762854,"uid":271413,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T02:33:37.000Z","msg":"搞大學咪即係搞死未來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98360c5cd9ab27483c7c48fa4cd374dd8114ccce","tid":1762854,"uid":138707,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T03:56:41.000Z","msg":"到時醫護人手更加短缺，輪候時間更長，就可以講政府同民建聯一手搞出黎。"}]}